subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: No. 3 Roger Federer was upset by 13th-seeded Jo-Wilfried Tsonga, 7-6 (3), 4-6, 6-1, leaving No. 1 Novak Djokovic as the last of the top four seeds at the Masters Series event in Montreal.
